                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5583" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0178</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8721 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北元化工的混合所有制：从创始人到董事会的控制权演变</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beiyuan Chemical Industry Group: The Evolution From Founder’s Control to Control of The Board</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">褚志远，张红芳（通讯作者），张丹妍，白闫洁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西北元化工集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制；控制权；公司治理；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">mixed-ownership, corporate control, corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了北元化工在混合所有制框架下走过的公司治理路径。北元化工以民营资本起步进入PVC行业，通过联合地方民营企业实现增资扩股并解决了企业生存问题。在项目扩建时与地方国企陕煤化集团合作，并成功引入陕煤化集团实现更大规模增资扩股，成为亚洲单体最大的PVC制造商，最终成长为总资产超百亿的大型现代产业集团企业。从小型民营企业到大型混合所有制集团，北元化工在发展壮大的同时，企业控制权经历了从创始人到董事会的多阶段演变，形成了公司治理的独特模式。在企业控制权演变过程中，创始人在企业中的位置和管理角色的转变成为混合所有制改革的一条主线。创始人在关键时间节点上的退出，不仅维护了混合所有制治理结构，而且推动了经理人职业化进程，既保障了定力，也激发了活力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the path of corporate governance under the framework of mixed-ownership in Shaanxi Beiyuan Chemical Industry Group. Beiyuan started to enter the PVC industry with private capital, and through united local private enterprises to achieve capital increase and share expansion to solve the problem of enterprise survival issues. During project expansion, Beiyuan cooperate with local state-owned enterprise Shaanxi Coal and Chemical Industry Group, and successfully bring in Shaanxi Coal and Chemical Industry Group to achieve larger capital increase and share expansion, and then become the largest PVC manufacturer in Asia, and eventually grow into a large modern industrial group enterprise with total assets exceeding 10 billion. While Beiyuan has grown and developed from a small private enterprise to a large mixed-ownership group, corporate control has undergone multiple stages of evolution from founder to board of directors, thus forming a unique model of corporate governance. During the evolution of corporate control, the founder&#39;s position and managing role in Beiyuan has become a main line of mixed-ownership reformation. The founder&#39;s withdrawal at the critical time not only maintains the mixed-ownership governance structure, but also promotes the professional process of managers, which guarantees the stability and stimulates the vitality at the same time.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制 公司控制权及其演变理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
